no adónde vino la fuerza mía,

194
00:09:05,000 --> 00:09:06,000
y adónde vino eso,

195
00:09:06,000 --> 00:09:07,000
no puedes.

196
00:09:07,000 --> 00:09:09,000
A mí no me van a matar.

197
00:09:19,000 --> 00:09:22,000
